Use the Playfair cipher to encipher the message "The key is hidden under the door pad". The secret key can be made by filling the first and part of the second row with the word "GUIDANCE" and filling the rest of the matrix with the rest of the alphabet. Use a Hill cipher to encipher the message "We live in an insecure world". Use the following key: ùêæ = [03 03 07]
import numpy as np

def hill_cipher_encrypt(plaintext, key_matrix):
    plaintext = plaintext.replace(" ", "").lower()
    key_matrix = np.array(key_matrix)
    if len(plaintext) % 2 != 0:
        plaintext += 'x'
    ciphertext = ''
    for i in range(0, len(plaintext), 2):
        vector = np.array([[ord(plaintext[i]) - 97], [ord(plaintext[i+1]) - 97]])
        encrypted_vector = np.dot(key_matrix, vector) % 26
        ciphertext += ''.join(chr(c + 97) for c in encrypted_vector.flatten())
    return ciphertext
